Package: com.jcatalog.grailsflow.search

[Groovy] Interface DisplayParameter

  • Interface for supporting configurable UI for showing search results

    Authors:
    Maria Voitovich

    • Method Detail

      • java.lang.String getDisplayTemplate()

        GSP template that renders display parameter value. Template parameters: - value -- display parameter value for current searchResultItem

        Returns:
        path to GSP template

      • java.lang.Object getDisplayValue(java.lang.Object searchResultItem)

        Parameters:
        searchResultItem
        Returns:
        object to pass to displayTemplate (if specified) or to render on the UI (if displayTemplate is not specified)

      • java.lang.String getName()

        Name of the display parameter. Name is used as column label. If DisplayParameter is sortable and then name is also used as value for sort parameter

        Returns:
        name

      • boolean isSortable()

        Indicates whether search results can be sorted by this parameter
